---
import SubpageLayout from '../../../layouts/SubpageLayout.astro';
---

<SubpageLayout
  lang="en"
  title="Process Optimisation"
  subtitle="Deep-dive into your business processes. Where are the automation opportunities? Which bottlenecks can AI solve?"
  seoDescription="AI Process Analysis: discover where automation and AI add value in your processes. Workflow mapping, bottleneck analysis and concrete gains. By AI Heroes."
  accentColor="red"
  pillarBadge="Consulting"
  ctaLabel="Schedule a consultation"
  trustedBy={["Medux", "OLX Poland", "Prosus"]}
>
  <div class="prose prose-lg max-w-none">
    <h2 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-6">Know where you're leaving opportunities on the table</h2>

    <p class="text-stone-600 leading-relaxed mb-8">
      Every organisation has processes that cost time and money but could be better. The question is: which ones? And where does AI truly make a difference versus a simpler solution? Our process analysis maps your workflows, identifies bottlenecks and quantifies the potential gains.
    </p>

    <div class="bg-stone-50 p-6 md:p-8 mb-8 border-l-4 border-brand-red not-prose">
      <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-3">What we analyse</h3>
      <ul class="space-y-2 text-stone-600 list-disc ml-5">
        <li>Current workflows and process steps</li>
        <li>Time spent per activity and employee</li>
        <li>Bottlenecks, duplicate work and manual actions</li>
        <li>Data flowing through processes (quality, availability)</li>
        <li>Existing tooling and automation</li>
        <li>Opportunities for AI versus traditional automation</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">Our approach</h3>
    <div class="space-y-4 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">1</div><div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark">Process mapping</h4><p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">We map current processes through interviews, observation and data analysis.</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">2</div><div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark">Bottleneck analysis</h4><p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Where is time lost? Which steps are error-prone? Where is manual work redundant?</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">3</div><div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark">Quantify opportunities</h4><p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Per identified opportunity: expected time savings, cost reduction and implementation effort.</p></div></div>
      <div class="flex gap-4"><div class="flex-shrink-0 w-8 h-8 bg-brand-red text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center font-bold">4</div><div><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark">Priority list</h4><p class="text-stone-600 text-sm">Ranked by impact versus effort, so you know where to start.</p></div></div>
    </div>

    <h3 class="text-xl font-serif text-brand-dark mb-4">What you get</h3>
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Process map</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Visual overview of your current workflows with pain points highlighted.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Opportunity register</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">List of AI and automation opportunities, quantified and prioritised.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Impact estimate</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Per opportunity: expected hours, cost and quality gains.</p></div>
      <div class="p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><h4 class="font-bold text-brand-dark mb-2">Recommendations</h4><p class="text-sm text-stone-600">Concrete next steps: start building, develop a business case first, or training.</p></div>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-6 mb-8 not-prose">
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">3-5 days</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Timeline</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">From €5,000</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Investment</div></div>
      <div class="text-center p-6 bg-white border border-stone-200"><div class="text-3xl font-serif text-brand-red mb-2">Prioritised</div><div class="text-sm text-stone-500 uppercase tracking-wider">Opportunity register</div></div>
    </div>

    <div class="dark-box-content bg-brand-dark p-8 border-l-4 border-brand-blue my-8 not-prose">
      <h3>From analysis to action</h3>
      <p>Process analysis is the foundation. Work out opportunities with a <a href="/en/services/business-case-development" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">Business Case</a> or take a broader view with <a href="/en/services/opportunity-scouting" class="text-white underline underline-offset-2 hover:text-white/80">Opportunity Scouting</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</SubpageLayout>
